<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear <%= @offer[:applicant][:first_name] %> <%= @offer[:applicant][:last_name] %>,</p>
    <p>
      We would like to offer you a position as a TA for <%= @offer[:position] %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please click the link below to view your offer and accept or reject it:<br/>
      <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Have a great day!</p>
    <p>PS. we've noticed that some browsers don't display the contract
    properly. Please try using chrome. If you have any troubles please
    contact tacoord@cs.toronto.edu. Sorry for any inconvenience.</p>
    
  </body>
</html>
